Suggestions

1. Sales reps should be empowered with the right tools, such as ensuring that the reps have access to daily sales activity through sales CRM. This will help the sales reps to have continuous visibility into their performance and to daily sales activity progress.

 2. The sales reps that are doing well should let the others know what strategies they are using.
